COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent
v.
Carlos Gene MOOSE, Jr., Petitioner No. 526 MAL 2015 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. Decided: February 23, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 23rd day of February, 2018, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is GRANTED. The order of the Superior Court is VACATED, and the matter is REMANDED to the Superior Court for consideration in light of Commonwealth v. Muniz, 164 A.3d 1189 (Pa. 2017).
